OL,5, A man who whose son died from an       
OL,6, allergic reaction to restaurant food   
OL,7, says he is waiting with "bated breath" 
OL,8, for a key food policy decision.        
OL,10,FPaul Carey's son Owen, from East       
OL,11,FSussex, died after unwittingly eating  
OL,12,Fdairy at a London burger bar in 2017.  
OL,14,FMr Carey wants to see the introduction 
OL,15,Fof Owen's Law to make the listing of   
OL,16,Fallergens on menus a legal requirement.
OL,18,FThe Food Standards Agency (FSA) said   
OL,19,Fits board will discuss its proposals on
OL,20,F13 December.                           
